spec_data.Name: kdeutils-minimal
spec_data.Description:
Minimal set of utilites for KDE 4.
Includes:
  * ark: tar/gzip archive manager
  * kcalc: scientific calculator
  * kdf: view disk usage
  * kgpg: gpg gui
  * ktimer: task scheduler
  * kwallet: kde wallet management tool
